%C3%A2u/poem-6huSycJjEU8trX3JXuC-2w">Tây lâu - 西樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-C%E1%BB%A7ng/author-fHbHbfl-NH8NLQqLmIcmbQ">Tăng Củng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-B%E1%BA%A5t-%C6%AF%E1%BB%9Bc/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-d%E1%BA%A1-du/poem-fV0O3R5icOx6zVz7x-_dng">Trường An dạ du - 長安夜遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-B%E1%BA%A5t-%C6%AF%E1%BB%9Bc/author-pNrHAYzUWGvxjTFtkyj7JQ">Viên Bất Ước</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%83n-Anh/T%E1%BB%ADu-tuy%E1%BB%81n-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-_ZgchEjBf1StanM6dnFd8w">Tửu tuyền tử - 酒泉子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%83n-Anh/author-to-UkdFjJeg6pwDSfG5oNA">Ngô Văn Anh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
